      <S N="ReleaseNotes">## [3.0.2] - 2025-12-05_x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_### Added_x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_- DnsServerDsc_x000D__x000A_  - Added new resource_x000D__x000A_    - _DnsRecordTxt_ - resource to manage DNS TXT records ([issue #150](https://github.com/dsccommunity/DnsServerDsc/issues/150))._x000D__x000A_    - _DnsRecordTxtScoped_ - resource to manage DNS TXT records ([issue #296](https://github.com/dsccommunity/DnsServerDsc/issues/296))._x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_### Fixed_x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_- DnsServerSetting_x000D__x000A_  - Set-TargetResource was not correctly retrieving current settings from remote computers._x000D__x000A_  - Updated comment based help for various settings to include allowed values in decimal._x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_### Changed_x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_- DnsServerSetting_x000D__x000A_  - Allow MaximumUdpPacketSize to be read/write. Fixes [issue #307](https://github.com/dsccommunity/DnsServerDsc/issues/307)._x000D__x000A_  - Add input validation to RemoteIPv4RankBoost, RemoteIPv6RankBoost, MaximumRodcRsoQueueLength,_x000D__x000A_    MaximumRodcRsoAttemptsPerCycle, TcpReceivePacketSize, MaximumUdpPacketSize.</S>
